WEBVTT

1
00:12:38.048 --> 00:12:40.797
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">We've got Yankee tanks
coming in from the plains.</font>

2
00:12:40.923 --> 00:12:43.297
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">We've lost most of our night vision</font>

3
00:12:43.422 --> 00:12:46.839
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">and have only a few
anti-tank missiles left.</font>

4
00:12:46.965 --> 00:12:51.047
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Put your best men into hunter
groups armed with RPG's.</font>

5
00:12:51.381 --> 00:12:54.338
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Have your men dig holes
100 meters apart.</font>

6
00:12:54.464 --> 00:13:00.963
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Wait until the Yankees
approach to strike</font>

7
00:13:01.089 --> 00:13:04.463
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">then attack them in force.</font>

8
00:13:04.714 --> 00:13:05.713
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Yes, Colonel Bella.</font>

9
00:13:07.005 --> 00:13:09.505
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I want some anti-aircraft here.</font>

10
00:13:09.631 --> 00:13:11.213
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">We're working on it, sir.</font>

11
00:13:11.381 --> 00:13:14.712
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">This... This is a madhouse!</font>

12
00:13:14.964 --> 00:13:16.546
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Do you want to see me?</font>

13
00:13:16.672 --> 00:13:21.004
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Yes... Yes.
Go to the sporting goods store.</font>

14
00:13:21.131 --> 00:13:25.130
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">From the files, obtain form 4473.</font>

15
00:13:25.255 --> 00:13:29.004
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">These will contain
descriptions of weapons</font>

16
00:13:29.131 --> 00:13:31.587
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">and lists of private ownership.</font>

17
00:34:31.595 --> 00:34:33.386
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Oh, how beautiful.</font>

18
00:34:45.845 --> 00:34:47.177
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">What is written here?</font>

19
00:34:49.054 --> 00:34:51.427
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You studied English. Translate.</font>

20
00:34:52.261 --> 00:34:55.177
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">American history.
I know this well.</font>

21
00:34:59.595 --> 00:35:02.677
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">"Arapaho National Battlefield.</font>

22
00:35:03.386 --> 00:35:05.469
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Here was a great peasant uprising</font>

23
00:35:05.677 --> 00:35:09.968
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">in 1908 of wild Indians.</font>

24
00:35:10.095 --> 00:35:14.010
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">They were crushed by
President Theodore Roosevelt,</font>

25
00:35:14.136 --> 00:35:19.219
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">leading imperialist armies and cowboys.</font>

26
00:35:19.344 --> 00:35:23.927
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">The battle lasted all winter.
More than 35,000 were killed.</font>

27
00:35:24.053 --> 00:35:28.218
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">It was the greatest battle
of the American West."</font>

28
00:35:28.677 --> 00:35:29.802
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Bravo!</font>

29
00:35:30.677 --> 00:35:33.301
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Yuri, stay here.
I'll take a photo of you.</font>

30
00:35:38.802 --> 00:35:40.301
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">African baboon.</font>

31
00:35:41.760 --> 00:35:42.926
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Now you.</font>

32
00:35:45.843 --> 00:35:47.509
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Come here, my friend.</font>

33
00:35:51.260 --> 00:35:52.926
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Hurry up, you fool.</font>

34
00:36:05.510 --> 00:36:07.092
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Look at me, Yuri.</font>

35
00:36:13.009 --> 00:36:16.467
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Look. Look what I've found.
An arrow.</font>

36
00:36:16.967 --> 00:36:18.592
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">An Indian arrow.</font>

37
00:36:18.717 --> 00:36:24.008
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I did not know the Indians used steel.</font>

38
00:36:24.134 --> 00:36:27.674
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Sure, you fool, they used the melted
sabers of Federalist Cossacks.</font>

39
00:36:27.801 --> 00:36:29.716
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">What a philosopher you are.</font>

40
00:36:29.842 --> 00:36:31.925
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Did these Indians work in plastic, too?</font>

41
00:36:32.051 --> 00:36:37.508
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You idiot, this is bone, polished to
a high sheen. There must be more.</font>

42
00:36:41.801 --> 00:36:42.633
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Look.</font>

43
00:36:46.925 --> 00:36:49.716
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Watch out! She has a weapon.</font>

44
00:36:51.258 --> 00:36:52.924
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Stop, damn it!</font>

45
00:36:58.342 --> 00:37:00.049
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Quickly. Catch him!</font>

46
00:37:12.508 --> 00:37:13.256
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Stop!</font>

47
00:37:21.049 --> 00:37:22.340
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Help me, comrades.</font>

48
00:37:28.508 --> 00:37:30.131
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I'm dying.</font>

49
00:38:30.714 --> 00:38:33.755
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">God help me!</font>

50
00:40:59.752 --> 00:41:02.542
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">From now on</font>

51
00:41:03.251 --> 00:41:07.750
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">all troops are forbidden to travel</font>

52
00:41:07.876 --> 00:41:11.708
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">outside secured areas</font>

53
00:41:11.834 --> 00:41:14.125
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">in any group smaller than squad size.</font>

54
00:41:16.168 --> 00:41:18.042
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Then call Bratchenko.</font>

55
00:41:18.168 --> 00:41:24.167
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Tell him Sector Eight is now active.</font>

56
00:41:24.334 --> 00:41:25.750
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Right away, Colonel Bella.</font>

57
00:41:26.334 --> 00:41:29.000
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">And I want some interrogations made,</font>

58
00:41:29.125 --> 00:41:32.208
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">starting with the mayor.</font>

59
00:41:32.334 --> 00:41:36.208
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I'm sick of his... pleasantries.</font>

60
00:41:36.334 --> 00:41:38.708
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Consider it done.</font>

61
00:47:01.325 --> 00:47:03.783
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Take gasoline.</font>

62
00:47:09.575 --> 00:47:12.532
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Hey, girl, what are you doing here?</font>

63
00:47:12.824 --> 00:47:15.948
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Hey, beautiful, where are you going?</font>

64
00:47:16.908 --> 00:47:19.365
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Forget the broad, just get her stuff.</font>

65
00:47:23.657 --> 00:47:25.782
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Where are you going?</font>

66
00:47:26.158 --> 00:47:29.281
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You're so beautiful.
Wait. What's wrong with you?</font>

67
00:47:39.616 --> 00:47:41.281
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Let's get her!</font>

68
00:48:49.322 --> 00:48:51.237
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">It's cut! It's cut!</font>

69
00:49:51.987 --> 00:49:55.028
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I've seen this before.</font>

70
00:49:55.154 --> 00:49:57.444
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Nicaragua, San Salvador,</font>

71
00:49:57.570 --> 00:50:02.028
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Cambodia, Angola, and Mexico.</font>

72
00:50:03.028 --> 00:50:05.235
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">But these are my men!</font>

73
00:50:30.236 --> 00:50:32.276
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">What is a Wolverine?</font>

74
00:50:32.402 --> 00:50:37.069
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">A small animal, like a badger,
but terribly ferocious.</font>

75
00:50:37.194 --> 00:50:42.818
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">It is also the name of the local
school sports collective.</font>

76
00:50:42.985 --> 00:50:44.193
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">They're beasts, Ernesto.</font>

77
00:50:44.319 --> 00:50:48.526
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You must kill every one
of them eventually.</font>

78
00:50:48.652 --> 00:50:52.359
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">It's the same as Afghanistan.</font>

79
00:50:52.486 --> 00:50:53.942
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">They'll never stop.</font>

80
00:50:54.902 --> 00:50:59.817
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Look. I was always on the
side of the insurgents.</font>

81
00:50:59.943 --> 00:51:02.484
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I have no experience in these matters.</font>

82
00:51:02.610 --> 00:51:07.484
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">But it would seem necessary
to win the support of the people.</font>

83
00:51:07.610 --> 00:51:11.317
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">As our opponents used
to say in Vietnam:</font>

84
00:51:11.485 --> 00:51:14.442
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">"Win their hearts and minds."</font>

85
00:51:14.568 --> 00:51:16.983
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">And they lost, Ernesto.</font>

86
00:51:17.109 --> 00:51:18.609
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Of course, General.</font>

87
00:51:18.818 --> 00:51:22.983
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Things are paralyzed
at the front, Ernesto.</font>

88
00:51:23.151 --> 00:51:26.150
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Morale is crucial right now.</font>

89
00:51:26.318 --> 00:51:29.358
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Keep the men in the secured areas.</font>

90
00:51:29.485 --> 00:51:32.816
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You'll see how they forget
about these Wolverines.</font>

91
00:51:36.650 --> 00:51:38.025
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Are you all right?</font>

92
00:51:41.400 --> 00:51:43.108
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You were saying, comrade?</font>

93
00:51:43.275 --> 00:51:45.232
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Shut up!</font>

94
00:52:00.400 --> 00:52:02.524
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">What's going on here?</font>

95
01:03:30.964 --> 01:03:34.547
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Help! The Wolverines are attacking!</font>

96
01:03:34.673 --> 01:03:36.630
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Follow me! Quickly!</font>

97
01:05:05.129 --> 01:05:07.544
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Children did this.</font>

98
01:05:07.670 --> 01:05:09.045
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">It's rebels.</font>

99
01:05:09.170 --> 01:05:11.961
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">What rebels? They're bandits.</font>

100
01:05:15.628 --> 01:05:18.753
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Every time they shoot,
the revolution grows.</font>

101
01:05:18.879 --> 01:05:22.127
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I know. I was a partisan.</font>

102
01:05:22.295 --> 01:05:26.461
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">And what are you now?</font>

103
01:05:27.336 --> 01:05:29.793
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Now I'm like you.</font>

104
01:05:30.462 --> 01:05:32.461
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">A policeman.</font>

105
01:17:13.109 --> 01:17:14.774
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Attention!</font>

106
01:17:26.108 --> 01:17:28.274
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Be seated, comrades.</font>

107
01:17:34.858 --> 01:17:39.898
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">What I despise most about warfare
is the hypocrisy it often breeds.</font>

108
01:17:40.316 --> 01:17:43.690
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I've heard euphemisms that
we are containing the enemy,</font>

109
01:17:44.191 --> 01:17:47.357
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">that our sector of
pacification is growing.</font>

110
01:17:48.482 --> 01:17:50.940
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">These are the tactics of the lie.</font>

111
01:17:51.315 --> 01:17:54.481
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Lies have the stench
of death and defeat.</font>

112
01:17:57.482 --> 01:18:03.273
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You can only win a war by
exterminating the enemy.</font>

113
01:18:05.441 --> 01:18:07.481
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Do you know who we are fighting?</font>

114
01:18:10.482 --> 01:18:13.314
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">We are fighting Wolverines.</font>

115
01:18:14.773 --> 01:18:17.481
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Small, ferocious animals.</font>

116
01:18:18.815 --> 01:18:21.023
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">For them, you need a hunter.</font>

117
01:18:21.815 --> 01:18:25.772
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">And you know... I am the hunter.</font>

118
01:18:31.273 --> 01:18:33.605
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">From this moment on</font>

119
01:18:33.732 --> 01:18:38.605
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">there will be no further
reprisals against civilians.</font>

120
01:18:38.773 --> 01:18:40.147
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">This is stupid.</font>

121
01:18:43.231 --> 01:18:45.147
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Impotence.</font>

122
01:18:48.772 --> 01:18:50.105
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Comrades...</font>

123
01:18:50.856 --> 01:18:54.855
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">If a fox stole your chickens,</font>

124
01:18:54.981 --> 01:18:59.438
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">would you slaughter your pig
because he saw the fox? No.</font>

125
01:19:00.814 --> 01:19:03.479
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">You would hunt the fox.</font>

126
01:19:04.064 --> 01:19:08.271
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Find where it lives and destroy it!</font>

127
01:19:12.105 --> 01:19:14.855
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">And how do we do this?</font>

128
01:19:17.272 --> 01:19:19.187
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Become a fox.</font>

129
01:38:39.448 --> 01:38:41.531
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Comrade Colonel.</font>

130
01:38:45.031 --> 01:38:49.155
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I would estimate the
enemy body count at 12.</font>

131
01:38:50.615 --> 01:38:52.197
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Twelve.</font>

132
01:38:53.281 --> 01:38:54.947
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Wouldn't you agree?</font>

133
01:38:56.573 --> 01:39:00.364
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Twelve?</font>

134
01:39:04.489 --> 01:39:06.780
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I saw only one.</font>

135
01:39:10.572 --> 01:39:12.905
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">But they carry off their dead.</font>

136
01:39:13.115 --> 01:39:14.738
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Of course. Why not?</font>

137
01:39:19.406 --> 01:39:20.822
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">What do you think?</font>

138
01:42:27.025 --> 01:42:30.650
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I can't remember what
it was to be warm.</font>

139
01:42:32.817 --> 01:42:37.525
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">It seems a thousand years since
I was a small boy in the sun.</font>

140
01:42:39.650 --> 01:42:43.024
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">How did I come to this high,
desolate place</font>

141
01:42:44.358 --> 01:42:46.399
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">where there is nothing but loneliness?</font>

142
01:42:49.650 --> 01:42:51.190
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">So much is lost.</font>

143
01:42:52.942 --> 01:42:56.816
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I want to look into
your eyes and forget.</font>

144
01:42:59.108 --> 01:43:01.273
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">It all seems so far away.</font>

145
01:43:02.525 --> 01:43:06.691
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">A warm house where
my shadow never falls.</font>

146
01:43:08.358 --> 01:43:12.898
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Your long, black hair in my hands.</font>

147
01:43:15.524 --> 01:43:17.731
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">There is no more revolution.</font>

148
01:43:18.732 --> 01:43:20.564
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Only you to come back to.</font>

149
01:43:22.274 --> 01:43:24.356
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">I will post my resignation.</font>

150
01:45:24.896 --> 01:45:27.478
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">They're attacking the station!</font>

151
01:45:29.895 --> 01:45:33.894
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Everybody to the station!</font>

152
01:45:59.812 --> 01:46:01.435
<font color="#ffff00" size="30">Hurry, hurry!</font>

